<synopsis><code mime="text/x-python">
@returns(Clutter.TextDirection)
def get_default_text_direction()
</code></synopsis>
<p>Retrieves the default direction for the text. The text direction is
determined by the locale and/or by the &lt;varname&gt;CLUTTER_TEXT_DIRECTION&lt;/varname&gt;
environment variable.</p><p>The default text direction can be overridden on a per-actor basis by using
clutter_actor_set_text_direction().</p>

